{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_08_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 芽衣に負けない最高の提案",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の仕事帰り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the way back from work one day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の仕事はこれで終わりだが\nすずはこのまま真っ直ぐ寮に帰るのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's work is done‚\nare you heading straight back to the dorm‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.6000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ユニットバトルに向けて\n寮で芽衣と作戦会議をする予定ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’m planning to have a strategy meeting\nwith Mei at the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はいつもあんな調子で世話が焼けますから\n私が率先して引っ張っていかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei always needs to be looked after‚\nso I have to take the lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2762073912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく芽衣と限定ユニットを組むのですから\nやるからには優勝を目指しますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we’re forming a limited-time unit with Mei‚\nwe’re going to aim for victory!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.2333334287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "気合いが入っているようだな\n曲の構想はもうあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem motivated.\nDo you have any ideas for the song yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "具体的な内容はこれから考えますが\n私達の好きなものを詰め込んだ曲にするつもりですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll think about the details later‚\nbut I plan to make a song that includes all the things we love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9333334287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すずと芽衣の好きを詰め込んだ曲か……\nどんな感じになるのか、完成が楽しみだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A song filled with the things Suzu and Mei love…\nI’m looking forward to seeing how it turns out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、{user}さんに\nお願いがあるのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}-san‚\nI have a favor to ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "今後、ユニットのことで芽衣と話し合う時は\n事務所の会議室を使わせてほしいのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ when Mei and I are discussing unit matters‚\nI’d like to use the office conference room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.7666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "二人の予定に合わせてスケジュールを組んでおいたので\nこの日時で会議室を押さえておいてくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve already made a schedule based on both of our schedules‚\nso please reserve the conference room for these dates.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "きっと芽衣は途中でドーナツを食べたいと言い出すので\nそちらは私の方で準備しておきますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure Mei will want to eat donuts midway through‚\nso I’ll prepare those.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.2666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、私が仕切らないと何も出来ないんですから\n芽衣は世話が焼けますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ she can’t do anything without me taking care of things.\nMei is so high-maintenance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言う割に楽しそうだが……\nすずは芽衣とユニットを組めるのが本当に嬉しいんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ but you seem to be enjoying yourself…\nYou’re really happy to be in a unit with Mei‚ aren’t you‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "きゅ、急に何を言い出すんですの！？\n別に嬉しくなんてありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what are you talking about all of a sudden!?\nI’m not happy at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.2000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "大体芽衣は、いつもマイペースで、何を考えてるか\n分からなくて、急に突拍子もないことを言い出すし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei is always doing her own thing‚ I never know what she’s thinking‚\nand she suddenly says the most outlandish things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり私に抱きついたり、頭を撫でたりして\n振り回されるこっちはいい迷惑なのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She suddenly hugs me or pats my head‚\nit’s so annoying!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.0666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "……ですが、まぁ、初めての芽衣とのデュオですから\nちょっとだけ楽しみではありますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ well‚ it’s my first duo with Mei‚\nso I’m a little bit excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.7000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ほんのちょっとだけですわよ！？\nな、なんですの、そのニヤニヤした顔は！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just a little bit!?\nW-what’s with that smirk on your face?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん。二人は本当に仲良しだなと思ってな\nどんなユニットになるか、俺も楽しみだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. I just thought you two are really close.\nI’m looking forward to seeing what kind of unit you’ll be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "仲良しではありませんが……私達の実力なら\nスーパーユニットが爆誕するのは間違いないですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not close… But with our abilities‚\na super unit will be born without a doubt!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "私達の活躍、楽しみにしていてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please look forward to seeing us in action!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.3000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.3000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もうこんな時間か。そろそろ帰らないと……ん？\n会議室の明かりがついているが、誰かいるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s already this late‚ huh? I should head back… Hmm?\nThe light’s on in the conference room. Is someone there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.1333273252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……これではダメですわ……\nもっと斬新で革新的なアイデアじゃないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… This won’t do…\nIt needs to be a more original and innovative idea…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5511853211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
